rows.label: tev062101_MSG0001
rows.name: Does friend know why brotherpon Tatsu wears glasses?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0002
rows.name: ...Because Tatsu cannot see well? Bzzt! Wrong![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0003
rows.name: Glasses are for show. Tatsu is going for certain look.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0004
rows.name: Tatsu start wearing them to look more like dadapon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0005
rows.name:
But Tatsu not have same fashion sense as dadapon.
Tatsu look like total dweeb![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0008
rows.name: Is brotherpon Tatsu behaving?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0009
rows.name:
Tatsu better not be getting in hair of friends and
working up debt just to become heropon next year![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0010
rows.name:
Truth is, brotherpon Tatsu is unreliable,
and brotherpon Satsu sleep all the time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0011
rows.name:
Also, sisterpon Yoyotsu spend all day eating,
while brotherpon Gotsu always making up stories.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0012
rows.name:
Mumutsu is youngest, but only one who actually seem
to care about family. Pull it together, siblings! Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0017
rows.name: Meh! Why does Satsu always have to cause trouble?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0018
rows.name: Well, at least Mumutsu got to go on fun adventure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0019
rows.name:
That was first time Mumutsu got to go outside caravan
all by lonesome.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0020
rows.name:
If Mumutsu eventually become Nopon heropon,
Mumutsu can go to all kinds of interesting places![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0021
rows.name:
Mumutsu starting to see appeal of whole heropon
thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0025
rows.name:
Friend want to know why brotherpons and sisterpons
call Tatsu "Dadapon"? Okay.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0026
rows.name:
It is because family want Tatsu to become strong,
just like our real dadapon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0027
rows.name:
Even though dadapon is tuft-deep in debt,
dadapon work REALLY hard to pay it off without
any complaints. Mumutsu is so proud![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0028
rows.name:
Now Mumutsu just need to find boyfriend as strong as
dadapon and get married![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0035
rows.name: Are all Ganglion baddies gone?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0036
rows.name:
Then that means castle in Cauldros is empty now!
Future Nopon city secured![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0037
rows.name:
Mumutsu will be leader, of course.
Beautiful princess of Castle Nopon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0038
rows.name:
Gotsu can be honorary prince since Mumutsu always
have to look after Gotsu anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062101_MSG0039
rows.name:
Time to get down to princess training. *ahem*
Bow, worm! Attend to every need of Princess Mumutsu![ST:wait ]
